 productive terms. This\nputs coinductive methods in LP on par with productivity-based observational\napproaches to coinduction in ITP and TRS.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 24 Nov 2015 20:53:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 4 May 2017 07:54:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-05-05"}
